{"tid":156940,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"Banks - 那暗異迷離的女聲體驗","createTime":"2017-03-15T06:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T18:33:12.000Z","uid":18697,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a8d71ce8d0d03152476175cb6467495dde3f00e","tid":156940,"uid":18697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P2VdoJo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP2VdoJo.jpg&h=44405904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBanks，本名為 Jillian Rose Banks<br />\n生於1988年6月16日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7v2577.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7v2577.jpg&h=4a363757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因15歲時的家庭問題等問題，開始自學樂器及創作，希望藉由音樂表達內心世界。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/133836_a00ecbbcc2e72948042c13651ff0e094.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F133836_a00ecbbcc2e72948042c13651ff0e094.jpg&h=0b6b9f15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她的曲風多為黑暗迷離。歌曲與MV的配合產生出極具獨特、獵奇的感覺。<br />\n<br />\nBegging For Thread (From &quot;Goddess&quot; album)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Twix375Me4Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTwix375Me4Q&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=9bbae4aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Twix375Me4Q</a><br />\n<br />\nWaiting Game (From &quot;Goddess&quot; album)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JCT_lgJ5eq8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJCT_lgJ5eq8&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=1e0f58ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JCT_lgJ5eq8</a><br />\n<br />\nTrainwreck (From &quot;The Altar&quot; Album)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vSNqIerZBFs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvSNqIerZBFs&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=eb80df75\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vSNqIerZBFs</a><br />\n<br />\nFuck with Myself (From &quot;The Altar&quot; Album)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-99e4geCm2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-99e4geCm2w&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=e1765ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-99e4geCm2w</a><br />\n<br />\n內容出處：<a href=\"http://queen4551852.pixnet.net/blog/post/311736384-音樂人介紹──banks(beggin-for-thread)(更新gemini-f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqueen4551852.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F311736384-%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9%E2%94%80%E2%94%80banks%28beggin-for-thread%29%28%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0gemini-f&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=67e7e4dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://queen4551852.pixnet.net/blog/post/311736384-音樂人介紹──banks(beggin-for-thread)(更新gemini-f</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://saint1102.pixnet.net/blog/post/40268611-bbc-sound-of-2014-英國bbc新星預測\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsaint1102.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F40268611-bbc-sound-of-2014-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8Bbbc%E6%96%B0%E6%98%9F%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=d63bcf2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://saint1102.pixnet.net/blog/post/40268611-bbc-sound-of-2014-英國bbc新星預測</a><br />\n<br />\n其實開post係想睇下有冇同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0122ab1d7a18f060a1a6f550537a374db3b658","tid":156940,"uid":18697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6998f5f1df0409334bd8f0343a6af3a469be4abe","tid":156940,"uid":82867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"Beggin for thread 同Gemini feed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" 